TEXT.S: = Tjalja'avus = Gaga mniq Pingtung Rayyisyang ka alang Tjalja'avus. 341 sapah ka kneegu na sapah, 1,122 hiyi ka kana knhbragan na hiyi. Tnpusu seejiq o mangal 97% niqan 1,092 hiyi sp, rahuq na uxay tnpusu seejiq o mangal 3% niqan 30 hiyi koia. Kana ka kleegan seejiq ga, Paiwan93%, Amis1%, Rukai1%, ni rahuq na o2%.
